<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>SSGPT6 | Sovereign Intelligence & Infrastructure</title>
    <style>
        :root {
            --bg: #050b18;
            --gold: #c7a85a;
            --un-blue: #009edb;
            --glass: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.03);
            --border: rgba(199, 168, 90, 0.2);
        }
        body { margin: 0; background: var(--bg); color: #fff; font-family: 'Inter', sans-serif; overflow-x: hidden; }
        
        /* THE INFINITY GRADIENT */
        .hero { height: 100vh; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: center; background: radial-gradient(circle at center, #1b1f4a 0%, #050b18 100%); position: relative; }
        
        .matrix-grid { 
            display: grid; 
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr)); 
            gap: 20px; 
            padding: 50px;
        }

        .card { 
            background: var(--glass); 
            border: 1px solid var(--border); 
            padding: 30px; 
            border-radius: 15px; 
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            transition: 0.4s;
        }

        .card:hover { border-color: var(--gold); transform: translateY(-10px); }

        .slogan { color: var(--gold); letter-spacing: 5px; text-transform: uppercase; font-size: 0.7rem; }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<section class="hero">
    <div style="text-align:center;">
        <div class="slogan">Tiny AI Big Brain Black Box</div>
        <h1 style="font-size:4rem; margin:10px 0;">SSGPT6 CORE</h1>
        <p style="color:var(--un-blue); font-weight:bold;">Sovereign Hydro-Atmospheric Matrix</p>
        <a href="#matrix" style="border:1px solid var(--gold); padding:15px 40px; color:var(--gold); text-decoration:none; margin-top:20px; display:inline-block;">Enter the 135 Matrix</a>
    </div>
</section>

<section id="matrix" class="matrix-grid">
    <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color:var(--gold);">UNIT 012: HYDROL-STASIS</h3>
        <p>Real-time Water Bankruptcy Monitoring. Advanced Oxidation (AOP) Restoration Logic.</p>
        <small>STATUS: ACTIVE | 5.8 GHz SYNC</small>
    </div>

    <div class="card">
        <h3 style="color:var(--gold);">UNIT 001: PHARMA VAULT</h3>
        <p>Proprietary Medical IP Acquisition & Global Royalty Stream Management.</p>
        <small>VALUATION: $75,000,000.00</small>
    </div>
</section>

<footer>
    <div style="text-align:center; padding:40px; border-top:1px solid var(--border); font-size:0.7rem; color:rgba(255,255,255,0.4);">
        GNAIAAAC LLC © 2026 | PROTECTED BY SOVEREIGN NEURAL-LATTICE
    </div>
</footer>

</body>
</html>
